<D>__{well, isn't this a coincidence! i'm out for a little mornin' ride, and right in the middle of nowhere, i bump into general ulysses s. grant himself!}
<P>__{(leans over edge, mocking salute)}
<D>__{we've never been properly introduced. i'm dr. arliss loveless, formerly with the confederate army.}
<L>__{exterior promontory point day (intercut with tarantula:}
<A>__{bridge) cool and collected, grant lights a cigar.}
<C>__{president grant}
<D>__{yes, dr. loveless, what can i do for you today?}
